            "title": "盤中速報 - 華東(8110)股價拉至漲停，漲停價21.25元，成交75,576張",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華東(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8110:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8110\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8110-TW</a>)03日10:04上漲1.9元，股價漲停報21.25元，委買32,377張，成交75,576張。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>主要業務為CC01080電子零組件製造業。</p></section><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>華東(<a data-ga-click-item=\"TWS:8110:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://www.cnyes.com/twstock/8110\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">8110-TW</a>)近5日股價上漲14.5%，集中市場<a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/TWS/TSE01\">加權指數</a>上漲1.36%，股價漲幅表現優於大盤。</p></section><section><p><em>近5日籌碼</em></p></section><!--$--><!--/$--><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>三大法人合計買賣超：+9,431 張</li> <li>外資買賣超：+9,376 張</li> <li>投信買賣超：0 張</li> <li>自營商買賣超：+55 張</li> <li>融資增減：+1,636 張</li> <li>融券增減：+185 張</li> </ul></section></main>",
